Dialogue: 69,0:00:07.81,0:00:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:27.22,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What're ya doin' here, Shinpei?\N Ya came back?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I should be the one askin' ya!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That necklace...
Dialogue: 69,0:00:37.69,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was one-of-a-kind and she left it behind. But how?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:41.99,0:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio's dead.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:43.65,0:00:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We held a funeral for her two days ago!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:49.97,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer not her.\N
Dialogue: 69,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't be Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:55.39,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're ya sayin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't I alive?\N
Dialogue: 69,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:03.51,0:01:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's it saying?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This thing's a Shadow! No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:09.39,0:01:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Ya don't remember what happened to ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:14.00,0:01:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 69,0:01:23.69,0:01:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I... huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:34.01,0:01:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'don't remember what happened before coming here?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain...
Dialogue: 69,0:01:42.70,0:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot of pain.\N That's all I remember.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:49.84,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was underwater...\NEverything was going dark.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:58.60,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I did die!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what the heck am I?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A... ghost?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:08.00,0:02:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't ghosts float in the air?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:11.24,0:02:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it really think it's Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:15.87,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:19.88,0:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember just one thing.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My last thought was that I wished for somethin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished I could see ya one more time, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:31.06,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why ya came back?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That voice. That behavior.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it! What the hell?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:44.64,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like Ushio really {\i0}has{\i1} come back from the dead!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:54.25,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more thing I wanted to tell ya if I ever saw ya again.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I love ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I love ya, Shinpei!
