Dialogue: 69,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did she just say?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She l-loves me?\N What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:50.05,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're ya sayin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did dyin' make you go crazy?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:59.68,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my head's all fuzzy.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}D-Don't be fooled. Take a step back!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two days ago, Ushio was lying in a casket.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:13.25,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's ash now. She's no longer of this world.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:17.52,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That thing's pretending to be her.\N What the hell is it after?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did ya come here?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When ya die, ain't ya supposed to go to heaven?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's yer goal?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do y'all want?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I want?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, those fireworks.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me today's the 24th.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! O-Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There {\i1}is{\i0} somethin' I wanna do!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the festival with ya!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, hurry up!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't think of itself as a Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:10.23,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it really consider itself to be Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, I wanna play this game!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on! Why's it still in a swimsuit?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! Everyone's starin'!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somethin' smells really yummy.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat takoyaki!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't the time!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone we know sees ya?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I even supposed to explain this?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one, come all!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the biggest and cheapest octopus in our takoyaki.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes real good!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout it, sir?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we hafta hide here?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.\N Ain't Mio 'n' the gang comin' too?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see 'em.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:16.89,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the situation for a second, will ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, yer dead!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We held a funeral for ya two days ago!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 69,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothin'!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer a Shadow—
Dialogue: 69,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe yer a ghost. I dunno.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone can see ya, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What even are ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So yer sayin' I can't see my friends?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:38.50,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, just hide here until the festival's over.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, ya big dummy!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit spoutin' nonsense!\N Or I'll twist yer mouth off!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she punches before warning me?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's just like Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:00.98,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ended up talking with Ushio's Shadow for a bit.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:04.71,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About what I'd experienced in my two years off the island, \Nand memories from when we were younger.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio remembered it all.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember who my favorite author is?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it Nagumo Ryuunosuke?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One of his books became a movie, and we went to see it at Garden Park.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:21.82,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But for some reason, she had no memory of anything related to Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't even remember how she died.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya wonder what happened to Shiori?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Somethin' the matter with her?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it doesn't seem like she's acting to me.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, it's nothin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone call?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Mio.
