Dialogue: 69,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gimme!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's me!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mio? It's me!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:07.83,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I just heard my sister's voice.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That ain't possible!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Ya sure yer okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:19.04,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I must be hearing things.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:22.50,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya, Shin?\N The fireworks are over already.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're inside the shrine.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're starting the ceremony.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm close.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll run over.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Never ya mind! Y'need ta stay hidden!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll come get ya later.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:50.68,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'don't even know just how dangerous things are right now.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:54.89,0:09:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya once told me to protect Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna have any regrets anymore.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't never said anythin' like that.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There ya are, Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Took ya long enough! We were worried.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mountains!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:21.27,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my stomach suddenly started hurtin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mesopotamian culture.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Told ya he had to poop.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do ya look so proud?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On Hitogashima,
Dialogue: 69,0:10:36.54,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is a long-held belief that says a god dwells inside everything which drifts ashore.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That deity is Hiruko no Mikoto.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:45.94,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We call it Hiruko, the god of fishing.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any wreckage that gets washed ashore is gathered instead of discarded.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:54.28,0:10:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We send the god off in a ceremony called "omiokuri" and burn the items.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lot of people came to see it.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are easily a thousand here.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since we all watched the ceremony together.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio's watchin' too!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:13.21,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In heaven.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have even come to the festival after my sister's passing?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope she's here in spirit.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:29.13,0:11:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did ya want to talk about?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently,
Dialogue: 69,0:11:37.63,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother is going to confess to Mio today.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:40.34,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is he serious?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:44.48,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be so illogical sometimes.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:49.12,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes magic can happen, though.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:54.09,0:11:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not going to happen here.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mio
Dialogue: 69,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,already has someone she's in love with.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be the one to say.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:13.69,0:12:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tokiko!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, hey, Mio...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this probably ain't the time to say this.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:26.32,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I want you to hear it!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do love you, Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-With that said, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me protect ya!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He really said that!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hold on, Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you—
Dialogue: 69,0:12:51.94,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone's listening!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya even like about me?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:05.89,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy ya feel that way.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:11.26,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want us to be good friends!{rip sou}
Dialogue: 69,0:13:16.74,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I tell ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that sure was somethin'!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep yer chin up!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I said to stay hidden!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.29,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.47,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HD0AC36&\3c&HD0AC36&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.47,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 69,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That pretty hair...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:53.02,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:55.04,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—
Dialogue: 69,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wayghh!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:02.58,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not this Ushio of whom ya speak!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the warrior of love,
Dialogue: 69,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure—
Dialogue: 69,0:14:08.15,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, I got figured out in less than a second.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. You call that a disguise?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:21.20,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I really just wanted to see everyone's faces.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Toki help ya get dressed, Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya look great in that yukata!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not her.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are ya doin', Shin?\N Get away from it now!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my sister!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to let her go.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That hurts!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei! Explain!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What're ya thinkin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:22.17,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way ya can trade places with someone who's just had a funeral.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya never were planning on switchin', were ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't ya listen to me?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:34.47,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya deaf or somethin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's—
Dialogue: 69,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
