Dialogue: 69,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mio, I'm sorry for suddenly running off.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing, worrying her like this?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:29.61,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a minute? I've got somethin' I wanna ask ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:44.93,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I didn't even see it move!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this strength!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No human's this strong!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:52.92,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin, I heard ya recorded me.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be unthinkable.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:01.69,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you knew {\i1}beforehand{\i0} that I was comin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd ya know?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It knows!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It can't be...
Dialogue: 69,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yer kidding me.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did it kill all of them?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just how many victims have there been?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that traitor tell ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:44.11,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Traitor?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let this slide.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan's almost complete.\N There will be no interference.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigate.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How much does he know?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:56.15,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It cuts off and repeats.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories are quite strange.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have ya died?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:11.54,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my Shadow!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must have been copied there.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:19.62,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does that mean it has my memories up to that point?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! It's gonna update its memories!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're gonna find out!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:27.80,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They'll know that we're looking into the Shadows!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And stuff like Mesopotamian culture!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:31.41,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}No!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio. Why are these things popping up everywhere now?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:34.98,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to there being safety in busy places?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}No, damn it!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap, crap, crap!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Dammit! That's not what I should be thinking about right now!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get rid of him now, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gotta run...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}No!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Run, or they'll kill me!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}No!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone will be killed!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Shin?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:01.29,0:19:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a step back and think.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Mother tell ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If he dies, he can just try again, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the looping?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those memories for real?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't a video game, y'know.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't control it on his own.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:18.63,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we assume it's true, then everything makes sense.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:23.12,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to consider this issue in four dimensions.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a step back and look at our third-dimensional thinking from the fourth dimension.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:30.32,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't know it now, \Nhe might figure it out in the future.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:35.63,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You read way too many weird books.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:39.07,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can return to the 22nd with his memories intact,
Dialogue: 69,0:19:43.45,0:19:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then one day he will without a doubt become a hindrance to us.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:46.69,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't kill him.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not until everything's finished.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going up.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:57.29,0:20:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take his phone from his back left pocket.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Send some others down a level to grab Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the equipment storage behind a tent.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're late, we'll never hear the end of it.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:17.85,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... w-wait.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't able to protect anyone in the end.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:37.63,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lay a finger on Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! Just give it a rest, Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer bein' too cool.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother will be waking up soon.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:00.14,0:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, just stay still.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just sad seein' ya struggle so pointlessly, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I break yer leg, too?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:37.78,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The word "narezushi" isn't used on Hitogashima, is it?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never eaten it before.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from the ferry!
