Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.34,0:22:17.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Since I remember it all
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.30,0:22:21.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I'll alter my existence
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Take a breath, take a breath
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.94,0:22:28.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}The smell of a tepid tide, a choir of cicadas
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.89,0:22:34.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's not something that can be forgotten
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.32,0:22:39.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Being torn by engulfing regret is best avoided
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.85,0:22:44.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}So we're setting our lives aflame
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.64,0:22:55.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I can go on living just from the warmth of your palm if it's linked with mine
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.57,0:23:07.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}What will be left remaining of this all too short summer I wonder
Dialogue: 5,0:23:07.41,0:23:13.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's once in a lifetime, so we want to undergo a change
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.92,0:23:18.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,2000)}We want to change
